  "original_title": "\u0d91\u0da2\u0dcf\u0db4 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dbb \u0d8b\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0dca \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The organization of UNP anniversary celebrations is under the leadership of Ruwan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been decided to organize the work of the UNP's 76th anniversary celebration by a committee headed by Mr. Ruwan Wijayawardena, UNP Deputy Leader and Presidential Advisor.",
        "The United National Party 76th anniversary is scheduled to be held at the Sugathadasa Stadium in Colombo on September 6 under the theme \"Ekwemu\".",
        "On the occasion of the party's anniversary, all religious ceremonies are also scheduled to be held on September 4 in all the constituencies across the island."
      ],
